GWP and Energy Balance -

Wind/Electrolysis

Preliminary results: 
•	 GWP = 650 g CO2-eq/kg H2 
–  Only 5% of the greenhouse gas emissions from SMR 
•	 Energy balance = 20 MJ of H2  produced for every
